description:
HwItem: Table describing hardware items in a radio access network.

dateTime: Timestamp of record creation.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the hardware item.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2:  Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely redundant).
Id4:  Unknown identifier (likely redundant, potentially related to HwItemId).
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
HwItem.additionalInformation: Additional information about the hardware item.
HwItem.serialNumber: Serial number of the hardware item.
HwItem.equipmentMoRef: Reference to the equipment the item belongs to within the network management system.
HwItem.dateOfLastService: Date of the last service performed on the hardware item.
HwItem.hwType: Type of hardware item (e.g., SFP, Antenna).
HwItem.hwUnitLocation: Location of the hardware item within the site.
HwItem.productData: Product data related to the hardware item.
HwItem.manualDataEntry: Indicator of manual data entry status.
HwItem.vendorName: Vendor of the hardware item.
HwItem.hwCapability: Capabilities of the hardware item.
HwItem.hwModel: Model of the hardware item.
HwItem.hwName: Name of the hardware item.
HwItem.licMgmtMoRef: Reference to the license management object for the hardware item.
HwItem.swInvMoRef: Reference to the software inventory object for the hardware item.
HwItem.hwItemId: Unique identifier for the hardware item.
